Notice: This SDK is unofficial / community-maintained by Kyuzan Inc. and is
NOT affiliated with Turnkey, Inc. The cryptographic primitives are consumed
from the external KyuzanInc.Turnkey.Sdk NuGet package (source repo:
https://github.com/KyuzanInc/turnkey-sdk-csharp), itself a 1:1 logical port
of the official @turnkey/{crypto,api-key-stamper,http} TypeScript libraries.
The Turnkey port has been reviewed by automated multi-round LLM review
(Codex) in that repo, but has NOT undergone a paid third-party security
audit. Use at your own risk. See docs/security/storage-threat-model.md for
the storage-side threat model.
